﻿@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutSalesAndRefunds.cshtml";
    ViewBag.Title = "SalesAndRefunds";
}

<h1 class="text-center" style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; color: #81c408; font-weight: bold;">
    Sales and Refunds
</h1>
<p class="text-center" style="font-size: 14px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 30px;">Last updated: 17 March 2025</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555; text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    This Sales and Refunds Policy outlines the terms under which purchases may be refunded or returned and describes
    the responsibilities of both buyers and sellers when using TerraShop's platform.
</p>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">1. Sales Policy</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
    By completing a purchase on
    TerraShop, you agree to the following:
</p>
<ul style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <li><strong>Final Sale:</strong> All sales are final unless otherwise stated in specific product listings.</li>
    <li>
        <strong>Product Availability:</strong> If a product is unavailable after purchase, you will be notified, and
        a refund will be issued.
    </li>
</ul>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">2. Refund Policy</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
    Refunds are available under the
    following conditions:
</p>
<ul style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <li>
        <strong>Eligibility:</strong> Refunds can be requested within 30 days of purchase for eligible products,
        provided they are unused and in original condition.
    </li>
    <li><strong>Request Process:</strong> To request a refund, follow these steps:</li>
    <ul style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <li>
            1. Send an email to <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Contact")"
                                   style="color: #81c408; text-decoration: none;">team.terrashop@gmail.com</a> with
            the subject "Refund Request" and include the following details:
        </li>
        <ul style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <li>Your order number</li>
            <li>The product(s) you wish to return</li>
            <li>Reason for return</li>
            <li>Your contact details (email and phone number)</li>
        </ul>
        <li>
            2. Alternatively, you can contact us by phone at <strong>+0123 4567 8910</strong> during business hours
            (9:00 AM - 6:00 PM, Monday to Friday).
        </li>
        <li>
            3. Once we receive your request, we will process it and send you instructions on how to return the
            product(s) and receive your refund.
        </li>
    </ul>
</ul>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">3. Seller Responsibilities</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
    Sellers are required to honor their
    return and refund policies. Failure to comply may result in account suspension or other penalties.
</p>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">4. Disputes</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    In the event of a dispute between
    the buyer and seller, TerraShop will mediate the process. If necessary, we may intervene to ensure fair
    resolution based on our platform policies.
</p>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    We may update this Sales and Refunds
    Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it
    periodically.
</p>
<h2 style="font-size: 22px; color: #81c408; margin-bottom: 15px;">6. Contact Us</h2>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    If you have any questions regarding
    this policy, please contact us:
</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    Email: <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Contact")"
              style="color: #81c408; text-decoration: none;">team.terrashop@gmail.com</a>
</p>
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Phone: +0123 4567 8910</p>